               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440506-name-722" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-722" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-722" type="surname" value="POWRIE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-722" type="given" value="JOHN WHITE"></interp>JOHN WHITE POWRIE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a baker—the prisoner was in my service, and was employed to receive money for me—if he received 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 5 3/4 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on the 20th of April, he has not paid it to me, nor 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. on the 22nd—he should have done so on the evening of the day on which he received it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440506-name-723" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-723" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
